elements.2211.03098_bd1c196e5cfd5e3cf401748b70fbd: In this Letter, we have presented the proposal for the complete HDGSM of multi-photon system in arbitrary dimensions, resorting to the photonic hyperentanglement and QFT
elements.2211.03098_836b996df94cef68fbd0e55640480: However, we should acknowledge that this proposal is still theoretical, which is not easy to realize with the current technology
elements.2211.03098_650af3c3be0c0e8c601f98b2ac919: On the one hand, so far, the experimental preparation of high-dimensional hyperentangled GHZ state remains a challenge
elements.2211.03098_35aca4453b2b07306dd8e8f0ed262: Fortunately, both of the two-dimensional multi-photon hyperentangled GHZ state and high-dimensional two-photon hyperentangled state have already been realized in experiment
elements.2211.03098_a7b3cee1feadbe1566e9142906bc1: experimentally demonstrated an 18-qubit GHZ entanglement by simultaneous exploiting three different DOFs of six photons, including their paths, polarization, and OAM
elements.2211.03098_cec0c77b562ef9de24e066951b47d: have experimentally generated a high-dimensional hyperentangled photon pairs from two parallel spontaneous four-wave mixing processes with beam displacer interferometers
elements.2211.03098_6074dfa7e2c255c450a68a23de4d6: Therefore, we are confident that the high-dimensional hyperentangled GHZ state of multi-photon system will be efficiently prepared with the development of quantum technology
elements.2211.03098_60f3f1e58f403553b71765ee23441: On the other hand, the high-dimensional QFT on photon is required in our proposal, and it has been well studied in these years
elements.2211.03098_0319376ea8a36eb9d281b8f520e59: proposed a photonic QFT protocol, in which a single atom-coupled cavity system implements the photon-photon interactions and no active feedforward control is needed
elements.2211.03098_c73a4f021fa3e3e45db4380e4d9dc: Moreover, they also showed that a QFT with tens of photons may be possible with state-of-the-art cavity-QED systems
elements.2211.03098_d52c90492566a914f513da027befe: In conclusion, to our knowledge, the presented proposal is the first complete HDGSM scheme for entangled photons
elements.2211.03098_5c55b546dc9d89556a187af0877eb: Although it is not easy to accomplish in experiment at the present time, it is an important step toward the complete analysis of high-dimensional GHZ state
elements.2211.03098_89178f852f746a30314aae3de7078: We hope our proposal can be realized in the near future, and it will have useful applications in the high-dimensional quantum computation and quantum communication.
